message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper proposes a deep learning based method for mortality risk prediction from LDCT images, which involves computer vision (CV) techniques for image analysis and machine learning (ML) techniques for prediction. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence (AI) and neural networks (cs.AI), as well as medical imaging (cs.MED) and neuroscience (cs.NEURON) for the application of the proposed method in the medical field.
